              <span style="color: white; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold">VM</span>
            </div>
            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700">Voltrux Motors</h3>
          </div>

          <p style="color: #ccc; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6">Redefining Electric Luxury Trucks with cutting-edge technology and unmatched performance.</p>

          <div class="social-links" style="display: flex; gap: 15px">
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-block; width: 36px; height: 36px; background-color: #333; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-decoration: none; color: white; transition: background-color 0.3s ease">f</a>
